Pour coffee into large bowl. Add SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener; stir until SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener is completely dissolved. Add 1/2 cup of the whipped topping; stir with wire whisk until well blended. Pour into 8-inch square pan. Freeze 4 hours or until firm. Draw fork repeatedly through whipped topping mixture just before serving; spoon evenly into six dessert dishes. Top with the remaining 1/2 cup whipped topping; sprinkle with cinnamon. Store leftover dessert in freezer.